('bookkeeper-moex-01232', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', 'X4年10月1日丁公司以現金買回流通在外普通股1,000股為庫藏股票，買回成本每股$15，而11月15日 以每股$17出售半數庫藏股票，12月16日以每股$12出售剩餘之庫藏股票。請問X4年12月16日出售庫 藏股票時，丁公司應以「資本公積－庫藏股票交易」（借記或貸記）與金額進行如下之正確記錄：', '["借記：1,000", "借記：1,500", "貸記：1,000", "貸記：1,500"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4bb38bfd4ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0663b26b8679", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01233', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司採用曆年制會計年度，在X4年12月31日資產負債表中，該公司會計部門正斟酌一項報表表達問 題。該公司積欠之負債中，$200,000將於X5年2月16日到期，甲公司打算與銀行完成再融資協議，將 $200,000負債延長至X6年予以清償，而此協議已於X5年1月31日完成雙方之再融資合約，董事會並 於X5年3月31日通過X4年度之財務報表並宣布。請問此$200,000負債於X4年12月31日的資產負債 表應如何表達？', '["流動負債", "長期負債", "$100,000為流動負債，$100,000為長期負債", "$200,000轉為股東權益項目"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4bb38bfd4ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0663b26b8679", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01234', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '戊公司根據國際會計準則第16號「不動產、廠房及設備」，並於X4年12月31日對於設備進行重估價 模式，當時設備之帳面金額為$300,000，原始成本$500,000，累計折舊$200,000，而設備之公允價值為 $360,000。請問戊公司於X4年12月31日採用重估模式後，設備之帳面金額為：', '["$200,000", "$300,000", "$360,000", "$500,000"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4bb38bfd4ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0663b26b8679", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01235', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何項資產係屬投資性不動產適用範圍？', '["土地開發公司自用之土地", "人壽保險公司持有為賺取租金或資本增值之不動產", "電子公司持有為擴建廠房使用", "建設公司持有準備於營業過程中出售之不動產"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4bb38bfd4ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0663b26b8679", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01236', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '請問下列何者為財務報表的外部使用者？', '["公司經理人", "公司股東", "公司員工", "公司的董事"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4bb38bfd4ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0663b26b8679", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL)
